@node reg "DWaRFx À Registration"

As you know DWaRFx has always been freeware, and will remain so for ever. 
But now I have introduced a 'registration' scheme where people register 
DWaRFx so I can count just how many users are out there. The amount of 
users who register will help me see how many people are using my 
software and how frequently I should make updates etc.

So do it today, Register DWaRFx for FREE and show your appreciation. 
The amount of registrations I get will be counted up and used in 
future by me for articles etc.

 To register goto this URL and fill out the form :

